print(df.Size.value_counts())

def change(Size):
    if 'M'in Size:
        x=Size[:-1]
        x=float(x)*1000
        return x

    elif 'k'in Size:
        x=Size[:-1]
        x=float(x)
        return x
    
    else: return None

    
df.Size=df.Size.map(change);df.Size.value_counts()
